like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"入境處成日都同海關齊做嘢<br />\n真係打個電話已經搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b8d1be395c3a472d102e746e903d73bd1567d3","tid":290623,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵死啦裝修狗"},{"pid":"2955068e632b0cf53a4a9675382cbab2255c2db5","tid":290623,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"裝修佬真係無個好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93fe01908e78fe5ba5fc7d2a94cae8bdcac415e","tid":290623,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"搵黎做案例"},{"pid":"10839ac18220d040789a233d2de10472bf76a44b","tid":290623,"uid":46454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵黎做案例</blockquote><br />\n坐硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3bbdbe3a319a145eb98b778aa0dac64cc825c6","tid":290623,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵人裝修要無伏真係好撚難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以相熟朋友介紹真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n佢都係因為有相熟做海關先拉到人炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623b3f98d6308a2d6409260de4c6fdcaf0d570ad","tid":290623,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵黎做案例</blockquote><br />\n坐硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma