lor: red;\">费</span>都大撚獲</blockquote><br />\n食撚屎啦戅鳩仔"},{"pid":"aac6a882beb8988a8b9a67717f8108583e3c0fcf","tid":290623,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一家三口原住在政府宿舍，因臨近退休，去年花30萬元<br />\n<br />\n點解30萬可以買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？佢係公屋戶主？<br />\n<br />\n街外人買要150萬左右</blockquote><br />\n公務員退休還宿舍當綠表</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下<br />\n還左宿舍搬去公屋既話<br />\n間公屋可以買？</blockquote><br />\n佢個情況應該係退休申請公務員名額公屋<br />\n編比佢個間公屋係可出售公屋<br />\n之後立即用房署出售公屋價買左佢"},{"pid":"3b672cf6a17e21661677eb492ebe5ab127094eae","tid":290623,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一家三口原住在政府宿舍，因臨近退休，去年花30萬元<br />\n<br />\n點解30萬可以買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？佢係公屋戶主？<br />\n<br />\n街外人買要150萬左右</blockquote><br />\n公務員退休還宿舍當綠表</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下<br />\n還左宿舍搬去公屋既話<br />\n間公屋可以買？</blockquote><br />\n佢個情況應該係退休申請公務員名額公屋<br />\n編比佢個間公屋係可出售公屋<br />\n之後立即用房署出售公屋價買左佢</blockquote><br />\n如果你申請公屋時編左出售公屋邨<br />\n你都可以買入"},{"pid":"f9c571fd59fcaccdc7dd97450eb5c916f20d1b5e","tid":290623,"uid":121131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>退休，但個仔得中二</blockquote><br />\n公務員退休係咩年紀都可能用<br />\n尤其紀律部隊多提早退休<br />\n隨時佢想食長糧之後入私人市場"},{"pid":"842c46d43ad3d4666d241e3685d6719ce3da5bff","tid":290623,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一家三口原住在政府宿舍，因臨近退休，去年花30萬元<br />\n<br />\n點解30萬可以買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？佢係公屋戶主？<br />\n<br />\n街外人買要150萬左右</blockquote><br />\n公務員退休還宿舍當綠表</blockquote><br />\nisee 公務員真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f101a20740988d6dc416c41454aad797e733da10","tid":290623,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一家三口原住在政府宿舍，因臨近退休，去年花30萬元<br />\n<br />\n點解30萬可以買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？佢係公屋戶主？<br />\n<br />\n街外人買要150萬左右</blockquote><br />\n公務員退休還宿舍當綠表</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下<br />\n還左宿舍搬去公屋既話<br />\n間公屋可以買？</blockquote><br />\n前提本身間公屋可以買"},{"pid":"e62eb48be5dc4302905c0a8e409aa318e3527deb","tid":290623,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵人裝修要無伏真係好撚難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以相熟朋友介紹真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係錢既, 搵D有幾間分店又做得耐既室內設計公司實無問題.</blockquote><br />\n你肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好肯定law. 無舊客回頭好難養幾間鋪.<br />\n只係佢地一定唔會收最平, 但有個品牌, 有要求先好搵呢D.<br />\n<br />\n唔係就唔抵.<br />\n<br />\n一般裝修整水電真係要識人, 一般人唔會識睇.<br />\n其他其實跟緊D分幾期俾錢問題都唔大."},{"pid":"f59cd387c6753c458a3450c4a8169aeb63867d62","tid":290623,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d"},{"pid":"26f61c69c76cf6f4e9305215f65f7ee9c9dd8b80","tid":290623,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真 不過做人做事一樣 唔好揾埋老鬼做 揾後生既會好好多 有手尾同可以交yf"},{"pid":"e19239a16bdb724e32b2f7e71214bc5451dcaa8b","tid":290623,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d</blockquote><br />\n要自己跟不如落手同佢做埋好唔好"},{"pid":"bc257297c686e6b04028cfae85d22621172340a3","tid":290623,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真 不過做人做事一樣 唔好揾埋老鬼做 揾後生既會好好多 有手尾同可以交談</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f5c82aba1afb292804da44745cab7ba39d963a67","tid":290623,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋忌完美主義. 要好靚手工唔係貴少少咁簡單, 可以同一樣要多八倍時間做. 你俾唔俾得起八倍錢? 多D睇下其他人裝修或者有D自己動手做下比較下.<br />\n<br />\n要知D咩唔可以錯(入水, 去水, 防水etc), 執正個D就得.<br />\n<br />\n其他一眼望落去無大問題就OK."},{"pid":"17005a92e10f769d34699b744da5057a65a0e73f","tid":290623,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d</blockquote><br />\n要自己跟不如落手同佢做埋好唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時唔係老闆搵你笨, 係D CF偷懶.<br />\n<br />\n業主多D上去睇下, 睇下有無做足野都係保障自己既方法."},{"pid":"2fa5c0a64715930f7d191efdbadcd5c331586c9a","tid":290623,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵人裝修真係要睇彩數 仲要自己跟緊d</blockquote><br />\n要自己跟不如落手同佢做埋好唔好</blockquote><br />\nd錢你自己嘅 唔覺得跟緊d有咩問題"},{"pid":"bed858cdb6861abd9ecf1d5810153a8211a85f24","tid":290623,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾攻府整乜鳩優質的士狗計劃吖<br />\n整個優質裝修佬計劃就差唔多<br />\n一堆所謂裝修佬出嚟呃飯食"},{"pid":"9b2a3433a39745ee0d156cf2c906321ff90fbfb9","tid":290623,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾攻府整乜鳩優質的士狗計劃吖<br />\n整個優質裝修佬計劃就差唔多<br />\n一堆所謂裝修佬出嚟呃飯食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家有考牌都好左好多.<br />\n請後生可能好過請老野, 當然好既老野先係最值錢."},{"pid":"1b9c23fa621a134dc38b0cb23a84198255c98642","tid":290623,"uid":70238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"裝修唔揾相熟嘅可靠師傳，賴嘢機會好高。"},{"pid":"5ed64774efc9c270758ffe33f4debe123259ee19","tid":290623,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵人裝修要無伏真係好撚難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以相熟朋友介紹真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n相熟都要小心<br />\n我fd試過朋友介紹，d報價唔清唔楚，又貴其他一截，唔幫襯仲要發癲屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75c66ab6160eb24e954c8aee2c0315db25e93e0","tid":290623,"uid":14130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵人裝修要無伏真係好撚難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以相熟朋友介紹真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n相熟都要小心<br />\n我fd試過朋友介紹，d報價唔清唔楚，又貴其他一截，唔幫襯仲要發癲屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔熟唔食"},{"pid":"428fdc6b0cd70ecf271f8f98662c39c34d07c934","tid":290623,"uid":1423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"<ins>女</ins>水<div style=\"text-align: left;\">威糕糕[女/left]公司網[left]<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div></div>"},{"pid":"a39dc83acec8a5f0c45eec52bda3f3fdbaa9eabe","tid":290623,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵人裝修要無伏真係好撚難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以相熟朋友介紹真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n相熟都要小心<br />\n我fd試過朋友介紹，d報價唔清唔楚，又貴其他一截，唔幫襯仲要發癲屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔熟唔食</blockquote><br />\n有呢個可能<br />\n最好搵自己樓下有十幾廿年歷史既裝修公司再查一查口脾, 若大致上口脾OK才幫襯, 咁樣安全D, 開左廿年都唔收皮仲有名聲既, 唔會差得去邊"},{"pid":"8d8adaa574e260eacee94f2c52d7e8a489a2cfaa","tid":290623,"uid":100494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得海關肯做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 消委會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n消委會唔係政府機構，冇權冇勢<br />\n淨係可以點名批評商舖或幫你協調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯，消委會無權執法"}]}